Interface WorkspaceAware

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    UITaskManager
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ListTaskManager, SearchUIImpl

    public interface WorkspaceAware
    Components that need to be workspace aware should implement this interface.
    Author:
    Russ Tennant (russ@i2rd.com)

    • Method Summary

      Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      void initialize(Workspace workspace)
      Init for the specified workspace.

    • Method Detail

      • initialize

        void initialize(Workspace workspace)
        Init for the specified workspace. This is called before the object is operated on by the Workspace.

        NOTE: the Workspace calls this method. If you wish to register a WorkspaceAware instance with the Workspace call Workspace.register(WorkspaceAware).

        Parameters:
        workspace - the workspace.
